---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for Kitchen Equipment Canada directory."
>
  <header class="border-b border-neutral-950/5 bg-white">
    <nav class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
      <a href="/" aria-label="Homepage" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <img src="https://assets.ui.sh/marks/1.svg?color=emerald-600&text=KE&textColor=neutral-900&font=inter" alt="Kitchen Equipment Canada" class="h-8" />
        <span class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">KitchenEquipment.ca</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/contact" class="rounded-md bg-emerald-600 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-emerald-500 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-emerald-600">Contact Us</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm text-neutral-500 hover:text-neutral-700">&larr; Back to directory</a>

      <h1 class="mt-6 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">Last updated: April 8, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-sm text-neutral-600">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">By accessing and using kitchenequipment.ca (the "Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Site.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">Kitchen Equipment Canada operates an independent directory of commercial kitchen equipment suppliers in Canada. The Site provides company profiles, rankings, reviews, and service comparisons to help users make informed decisions about kitchen equipment suppliers.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">3. Rankings and Ratings</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">Company rankings on this Site are determined by an editorial scoring system based on multiple criteria including service range, customer reviews, industry experience, response time, pricing transparency, and certifications. Rankings represent editorial assessments and are not endorsements. Individual company scores may change over time as new information becomes available.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">We make reasonable efforts to ensure accuracy but do not guarantee that rankings reflect the current state of any company's services, pricing, or availability.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">4. User-Submitted Reviews</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">Users may submit reviews of companies listed on the Site. By submitting a review, you represent that:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5" role="list">
            <li>Your review is based on genuine experience with the company</li>
            <li>The information in your review is truthful and accurate</li>
            <li>You are not affiliated with the company you are reviewing (unless disclosed)</li>
            <li>Your review does not contain defamatory, abusive, or illegal content</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">All reviews are subject to moderation. We reserve the right to remove, edit, or decline to publish any review at our sole discretion, including reviews that violate these terms or appear to be fraudulent.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">The content, design, and structure of this Site are owned by Kitchen Equipment Canada. Company names, logos, and trademarks belong to their respective owners and are displayed for identification purposes only.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">By submitting a review, you grant Kitchen Equipment Canada a non-exclusive, royalty-free, perpetual license to display, reproduce, and distribute your review on the Site.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">The Site and its content are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or implied. We do not warrant that the information on this Site is complete, accurate, or current. We are not responsible for any decisions made based on information found on this Site.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, Kitchen Equipment Canada shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of or relating to your use of the Site.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">8. Company Listings</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">Companies are listed based on publicly available information and editorial research. If you represent a listed company and wish to update your profile information, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@kitchenequipment.ca" class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-500">info@kitchenequipment.ca</a> or use our <a href="/contact" class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-500">contact form</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">These Terms of Service are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Province of Ontario, Canada, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">10. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use of the Site after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">11. Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-pretty">For questions about these Terms of Service, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@kitchenequipment.ca" class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-500">info@kitchenequipment.ca</a>.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-neutral-950/5 py-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 text-center text-sm text-neutral-500">
      <p>kitchenequipment.ca. Independent commercial kitchen equipment supplier directory.</p>
      <div class="mt-3 flex justify-center gap-6">
        <a href="/privacy" class="font-normal hover:text-neutral-700">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="font-normal text-neutral-900">Terms of Service</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="font-normal hover:text-neutral-700">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Base>
